headline: 3 Insurance Stocks We Find Risky
summary: Insurance providers use their expertise in risk assessment to help protect assets while offering consumers peace of mind through comprehensive coverage options. But worries about an economic slowdown and potential claims deterioration have kept sentiment in check, and over the past six months, the industry’s return was flat while the S&P 500 climbed by 7.3%.
